# 🚀 HPC Task 2 - MPI Statistics

![MPI](https://img.shields.io/badge/MPI-Parallel_Computing-blue)
![C](https://img.shields.io/badge/C-99-green)
![Docker](https://img.shields.io/badge/Docker-Ready-blue)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-green)

---

## 📌 Overview

A high-performance parallel program for computing statistics on large datasets using MPI.

---

## ✨ Features

* Parallel processing using MPI
* Dynamic Hash Table (rehashing at 0.75)
* Supports large integers (int64_t)
* Handles 1GB+ datasets
* Docker support

---

## 📊 Statistics

* Minimum
* Maximum
* Sum
* Mean
* Frequency

---

## 🏗️ Structure

```bash
src/
include/
data/
output/
bin/
```

---

## ⚙️ Installation

```bash
sudo apt update
sudo apt install -y mpich gcc make
```

---

## 🔨 Build

```bash
make clean
make
```

---

## ▶️ Run

```bash
mpirun -np 4 ./bin/stats data/input.txt
```

---

## 🐳 Docker

```bash
docker build -t mpi-stats .
docker run --rm -v $(pwd):/app mpi-stats mpirun -np 4 /app/bin/stats /app/data/input.txt
```

